        <div class="rounded-pill bg-gray1 text-white my-1 py-1 pl-2 pr-md-5 pr-4 contact-button-text">
          <span class="d-md-none font-weight-bold">Nous contacter</span>
          <div class="d-none d-md-flex flex-column">
            <span class="font-weight-bold">Une question ?</span>
            <span>nous contacter</span>
